Privacy Policy for Pawnnect

Effective Date: Sept/17/2023

Thank you for using Pawnnect ("the App"). Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect the information you provide while using our App.

By downloading, installing, or using Pawnnect, you agree to the terms and conditions of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with these terms, please do not use the App.

1. Information We Collect
We may collect the following information from you:

a. User Identification Information:
User ID
Name
Phone Number
Location

b. Pet-Related Data:
If you provide information about your pets, such as names, breeds, medical history, or other related data, we may collect and store this information.

2. How We Use Your Information
We collect and use your information for the following purposes:

a. User Identification:
To identify you within the App.
To enhance your user experience.

b. Communication:
To communicate with you, including responding to your inquiries, feedback, or support requests.
To send you important updates, notifications, and promotional information (only if you opt-in).

c. Location Data:
To provide location-based services within the App.

d. Pet-Related Data:
To provide you with pet-related services and features.
To enhance your pet care experience within the App.

3. Data Retention
We are committed to protecting your data and have established the following data retention policies:

a. User Identification Information:
We retain user identification information indefinitely, but we do not share it with any third parties.

b. Pet-Related Data:
Pet-related data, such as names, breeds, and medical history, will be deleted after 90 days from the time it is provided by the user.

4. Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, no data transmission or storage system is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee the security of your information.

5. Third-Party Services
Pawnnect may contain links to third-party websites or services that we do not control. This Privacy Policy does not apply to the practices of those third-party websites or services. We recommend reviewing the privacy policies of those third parties.

6. Children's Privacy
Pawnnect is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe that we have inadvertently collected information from a child under 13, please contact us immediately.

7. Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will post any changes on this page, and the updated Privacy Policy will become effective upon posting. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically.

8. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at verygoodrove+contact@gmail.com.

By using Pawnnect, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and agree to its terms and conditions.
